prompt.title: Embedding for Mastering Book Language: Core Concepts
prompt.content: Book language uses three core concepts:  **What** (workflows, tasks, parameters defining the work), **Who** (personas defining who performs the tasks), and **How** (knowledge, instruments, and actions used by the personas).  It supports both flat (simple prompts) and full (structured with tasks and commands) formats.
